 â€¢ Just creating a NetworkPolicy doesnâ€™t block all traffic. It only affects pods selected by the policy.
 â€¢ Make sure your CNI plugin supports NetworkPolicies. Not all do!
 â€¢ Donâ€™t forget about egress rulesâ€”a lot of attackers exfiltrate data that way.

